overview.en: ADFS is the abbreviation of A Decentralized Financial System, ADFS is a decentralized financial system, aiming to create a global, open, free and fair block chain financial system, allowing users to be free from any restrictions such as race, religion, age, nationality, geography and so on. Without relying on any centralization, it is easy to use decentralized financial service systems such as storage, lending, payment, financial management, insurance and other financial derivatives services.

zh: ADFS是A Decentralized Financial System的缩写，ADFS是一个去中心化的金融系统，旨在创建一个全球、开放、自由、公平的区块链金融系统，允许用户能够不受种族、宗教、年龄、国籍、地理等任何限制，无需依靠任何中心化的情况下，轻松使用诸如，存储、借贷、支付、理财、保险等金融衍生品服务的去中心化金融服务系统。
